$GLOBALS["lang"]['If you are using Open-AudIT on Windows or if your NMIS server is not on your Open-AudIT Server (in the case of some Linux installs), you will need to supply access credentials and a URL to the remote NMIS - but that is all! Yes - Integrations between NMIS and Open-AudIT even work with Windows based Open-AudIT now!'] = 'Windows Open-AudIT istifadə edir və ya NMIS serveriniz Open-AudIT Server-da deyil (bazı Linux installs halda), uzaq NMIS-a daxil olmaq lazımdır - lakin bütün bunlar!  Yes - NMIS və Open-AudIT arasında inteqrasiyalar Windows based Open-AudIT ilə işləyir!';

