$GLOBALS["lang"]['Open-AudIT Professional has the ability to choose from a pre-defined list of discovery scan options, per discovery.'] = 'Qeydiyyat Professional hesab tarama variantları pre-defined siyahısı seçmək imkanı var, hesab.';

